---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "../components/container.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <Container>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-14 mb-20">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-3">
        <span class="text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm font-bold">Legal</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight text-slate-800">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Last Updated: February 24, 2025</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 prose prose-lg max-w-none prose-headings:text-slate-800 prose-p:text-slate-600 border-t border-slate-100 pt-10">
        <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
        <p>We only collect personal information that you voluntarily provide to us. This primarily includes your <strong>email address</strong>, collected solely upon your explicit consent when subscribing to our strategic reports or contacting us via our official forms.</p>

        <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
        <p>The information we collect is used exclusively for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>To deliver our intelligence insights and strategic alerts.</li>
          <li>To respond to professional inquiries or consulting requests.</li>
          <li>To improve the user experience and content relevance of AutoChina.org.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>3. Data Security</h3>
        <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data. <strong>We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to outside parties.</strong> Your data is processed only by authorized service providers for the purpose of maintaining our communication infrastructure.</p>

        <h3>4. Your Rights</h3>
        <p>You retain full control over your data. At any time, you may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your information. You may <strong>unsubscribe</strong> at any time via the link provided in our correspondence.</p>

        <p class="mt-10 text-sm text-slate-400 italic">Contact: contact@autochina.org</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>
